      <h2>Weather</h2>
      <p>The Dominican Republic enjoys a tropical climate with warm temperatures year-round. The country experiences a
        wet season from May to October and a dry season from November to April. Its beautiful beaches and lush
        landscapes make it a favorite destination for travelers.</p>
